# ‡∏≠‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏π‡∏•‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å CSV string ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô data.frame
df <- read_csv(csv_data)

library(htmltools)

# ‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á interactive table ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏ß‡∏¢ DT::datatable
df$Interpretation <- as.factor(df$Interpretation)

# ‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á custom CSS ‡πÇ‡∏î‡∏¢‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏∏‡πÄ‡∏â‡∏û‡∏≤‡∏∞ select ‡πÉ‡∏ô header ‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Ñ‡∏≠‡∏•‡∏±‡∏°‡∏ô‡πå‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà 4 (Interpretation)
custom_css <- tags$style(HTML("
  .dataTables_wrapper thead th:nth-child(4) select {
    font-size: 10px !important;
  }
"))
# ‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á DataTable ‡∏û‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏° filter row ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏Ç‡∏ô‡∏≤‡∏î font ‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏π‡∏•‡πÉ‡∏ô‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏á
dt <- datatable(
  df,
  options = list(
    pageLength = 6,
    autoWidth = TRUE
  ),
  filter = "top",
  width = "100%"  # ‡∏Å‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏ô‡∏î‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏Å‡∏ß‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏ï‡πá‡∏°‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏Å‡∏ß‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á container
) %>%
  formatStyle(
    columns = colnames(df),
    `font-size` = '14px'
  )

# ‡∏£‡∏ß‡∏° custom CSS ‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö DataTable ‡πÇ‡∏î‡∏¢‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ tagList ‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å htmltools
tagList(
